room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by Bozeman Breakout in Bozeman
room_address: 2304 W Main St, Suite 6 Bozeman, MT 59715
room_description:
It's the 1950's. You and your assembled team are all part of a single schizophrenic mind. Due to the lack of knowledge of mental health during this time you've been committed to The Asylum.
In one hour, your treatment will begin. A transorbital lobotomy... Can you escape before your mind is lost forever? Time is running out!
